'''栽培植物'''（{{lang-en|cultigen; cultivated plant}}）是由于人类的[[选育|选育]]或有意无意的[[杂交|杂交]]而产生的植物类群。<ref>{{Cite book|edition=9th ed.|last3=Cubey|last8=Jin|first7=V.|last7=Malécot|last6=Leslie|first6=A.C.|first5=M.H.A.|last5=Hoffman|first4=J.C.|last4=David|first3=J.J.|first2=C.|url=https://www.ishs.org/sites/default/files/static/ScriptaHorticulturae_18.pdf|last2=Alexander|pages=|year=|first=C.D.|title=International Code of Nomenclature for Cultivated Plants|last=Brickell|oclc=1029031329|isbn=978-94-6261-116-0|location=Leuven|date=2016|publisher=International Society for Horticultural Science|first8=Xiaobai|page=144|access-date=2020-09-20|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125190519/https://www.ishs.org/sites/default/files/static/ScriptaHorticulturae_18.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>分类单位为[[种|种]]的栽培植物也叫'''栽培种'''或'''培植物种'''（{{lang-en|cultivated species}}）。<ref name=":1">{{Cite book|title=生物多样性公约|author=生物多样性公约秘书处|publisher=联合国|year=1992|isbn=|location=|pages=|chapter=第2条. 用语|url=https://www.cbd.int/doc/legal/cbd-zh.pdf|access-date=2019-02-27|archive-date=2019-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190904155148/https://www.cbd.int/doc/legal/cbd-zh.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>栽培植物的演化进程受人类需求的影响，其种群维持又往往依赖于人类的栽培管理。<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":0">{{Cite book|title=Use and potential of wild plants in farm households|author=Food and Agriculture Organization of the United Nations|publisher=FAO|year=1999|isbn=9789251041512|location=Rome, Italy|pages=|url=http://www.fao.org/3/w8801e02.htm|chapter=Chapter 1. INTRODUCTION - What are wild plants?|access-date=2019-02-27|archive-date=2019-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190228003920/http://www.fao.org/3/w8801e02.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>栽培植物和野生植物并非总是泾渭分明，在完全的栽培植物和完全的野生植物之间还有各种过渡状态，具体情况依物种受人类干预程度而定。<ref name=":0" />

